What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Low Vision Aids Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The rising number of patients suffering from low vision conditions, the increasing occurrences of lifestyle diseases such as diabetes, the growing prevalence of geriatric population around the world, and the increasing need for advanced treatment methods are some of the major and critical factors that will likely boost the growth of the low vision aids market in the projected timeframe of 2023-2030. However, an increase in the number of research activities for the development of advanced devices, as well as the prevalence of well-established and improved healthcare infrastructure, will contribute to the growth of the low vision aids market during the forecast period.

